    "body": "@jorisvandenbossche : right, makes a lot of sense! And I now see [the following note](http://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/groupby.html#flexible-apply) I had missed: _\"apply can act as a reducer, transformer, or filter function, depending on exactly what is passed to it. So depending on the path taken, and exactly what you are grouping. Thus the grouped columns(s) may be included in the output as well as set the indices.\"_"
